<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_2501f10d-4b59-440a-b651-a64aee105281" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>G1D5</sptc><title id="_3f2b2513-fe68-49f6-9c0b-0fd80491f829">Swimming pool drainage</title><archive-num/><clause-variation variation="NT" variation-type="DELETE">NT DELETE Clause</clause-variation><subclause id="_9193be81-722e-4ecd-ada0-94bd3d3f794f" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_7b39d17f-5b0c-47f0-8258-192ded815da2">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_31cc77b0-78a0-4c15-a2b8-136addc2632d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool's</xref> pumped discharge must be discharged to the sanitary drainage system in accordance with AS/NZS 3500.2. </p></subclause><callout id="_fc680946-0177-4a9c-9931-ec4457acac38"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>Consideration should be given to the requirements of the relevant <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_f25dcdb2-8f08-4151-a7c9-02ca6dad2b4e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator</xref>. Where a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_f0fb7413-ce31-4935-bd89-66d7c4db0cc8" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator</xref> does not permit <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1487_0.7.0.xml#_4cbd9e00-0622-4dfd-9de4-913c80257732" id="_242acf22-92e9-4d8b-9a89-9e3ed0fd0b6d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">swimming pool</xref> discharge to the sanitary drainage system, a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1396_4.0.0.xml#_e3f95f1d-e1cc-4ab3-961d-c99a213a1de3" id="_06809f4b-d016-4ac6-ab80-7d932146461c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Performance Solution</xref> will be necessary to demonstrate the suitability of the alternative drainage method.</p></callout></clause>